gameobject

Class Primitive

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameobject.Primitive

  • public class Primitive
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a gameobject prototype which has not been created yet. You can create multiple gameobjects from this by using create()
    Author:
    jafi2
